ny%20turtles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-99-1743258466.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Arun%20addressing%20the%20people%20before%20the%20turtle%20walks%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-99-1743258466.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-99-1743258466-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-99-1743258466-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-99-1743258466-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-99-1743258466-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-417021%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20diverse%20group%20of%20people%20participate%20in%20the%20turtle%20walks%20conducted%20by%20SSTCN.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20SSTCN%E2%80%99s%20conservation%20efforts%20is%20a%20dedicated%20group%20of%20volunteers%20%E2%80%94%20students%2C%20professionals%2C%20and%20conservation%20enthusiasts%2C%20who%20devote%20their%20nights%20to%20patrolling%20Chennai%E2%80%99s%20beaches.%20For%20many%2C%20this%20experience%20is%20more%20than%20just%20an%20environmental%20effort%3B%20it%20is%20a%20deep%2C%20personal%20connection%20to%20marine%20life%20and%20a%20lesson%20in%20responsibility.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20coming%20for%20turtle%20walks%20in%202007.%20I%20was%20fascinated%20with%20turtles%20so%20much%20that%20I%20switched%20streams%20from%20an%20accountant%2