ia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FBihar-farmers-2-1715870736-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FBihar-farmers-2-1715870736-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FBihar-farmers-2-1715870736-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FBihar-farmers-2-1715870736-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350325%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPrabhat%20is%20associated%20with%2025%2C000%20farmers%20who%20earn%20double%20by%20growing%20crops%20like%20onions%2C%20mushrooms%2C%20baby%20corn%2C%20and%20sweet%20corn.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%204-5%20months%2C%20farmers%20doubled%20their%20income%20by%20investing%20Rs%204%20per%20kg%20and%20getting%20Rs%2010%20per%20kg%20from%20onions.%20%E2%80%9CEach%20farmer%20earned%20Rs%201%20lakh%20income%20per%20acre%20of%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20low-cost%20storage%20facility%2C%20farmers%20stored%20onions%20for%20six%20months%20from%20May%20to%20October%20in%202016.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20unit%20would%20be%20vacant%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20time.%20So%2C%20we%20introduced%20mushrooms%20for%20the%20utility%20of%20that%20part.%20It%20is%20a%20winter%20crop%20and%20was%20a%20perfect%20match%20to%20utilise%20our%20vacant%20facility%20in%20that%20period%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20switch%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F338206%2Fhow-to-start-a-mushroom-business-rajasthan-mba-dropout-jeevan-success-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emushroom%20cultivation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CGrowing%20mushrooms%20was%20completely%20opposite%20from%20traditional%20agriculture.%20In%20conventional%20farming%2C%20farmers%20bea