we%20do%20not%20lag%20behind%20progressive%20states%20like%20Maharashtra.%20In%20the%20coming%20years%2C%20I%20am%20planning%20to%20achieve%20this%20by%20helping%20farmers%20process%20their%20produce%20into%20value-added%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%20courtesy%20SumArth%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1756207800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FBihar-farmers-4-1-1715870841.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D492045%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20onions%20and%20mushrooms%20to%20strawberries%20and%20processing%20units%2C%20SumArth%E2%80%99s%20holistic%20model%20transformed%20farming%20across%20500%20villages%20%E2%80%94%20turning%20recurring%20costs%20into%20recurring%20income.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Gorakhpur%20Boosted%20Flood%20Response%20by%2065%25%20With%20a%20Smart%20System%20Combining%20Process%2C%20Tech%20%26amp%3B%20People%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20Canarys%20Automations%20Limited%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20monsoon%2C%20it%20was%20the%20same%20dreadful%20story.%20The%20water%20would%20not%20just%20flood%20the%20streets%3B%20it%20entered%20our%20homes%2C%20flowing%20right%20into%20the%20kitchen%20and%20living%20room.%20We%20were%20stranded%2C%20sometimes%20waist%E2%80%91deep%20in%20water%2C%20watching%20helplessly%20as%20our%20belongings%20were%20ruined.%20The%20floodwaters%20would%20remain%20for%20days%2C%20and%20often%2C%20the%20officials%20took%20time%20to%20help%20us%20out.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20is%20the%20recall%20of%20Ratna%E2%80%AFDevi%20from%20Ward%E2%80%AFNo%E2%80%AF12%20in%20Ashoknagar.%20Her%20experience%20is%20not%20an%20isolated%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYear%20af