l%20weaknesses%20and%20identify%20priority%20zones%20for%20drainage%20improvement%2C%20flood%20barriers%2C%20and%20urban%20redesign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheshadri%20summarises%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20DSS%20acts%20as%20a%20strategic%20engine%3B%20it%20offers%20insight%20not%20just%20for%20managing%20floods%20but%20for%20rebuilding%20city%20infrastructure%20intelligently.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120908.426_11zon-1754980764.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Early%20Warning%20System%20(EWS)%20plus%20Decision%20Support%20System%20(DSS)%20fuses%20multiple%20data%20sources%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120908.426_11zon-1754980764.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120908.426_11zon-1754980764-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120908.426_11zon-1754980764-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120908.426_11zon-1754980764-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120908.426_11zon-1754980764-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-485278%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Early%20Warning%20System%20(EWS)%20plus%20Decision%20Support%20System%20(DSS)%20fuses%20multiple%20data%20sources%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20prediction%20to%20protection%3A%20A%20fully%20coordinated%20approach%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20system%20operates%20through%20three%20interconnected%20stages%3A%20Predict%2C%20Prepare%2C%20and%20Protect.%20Each%20stage%20is%20operationalised%20through%20dedicated%20SoPs%20(Standard%20Operating%20Procedures).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cstrong%3EPrediction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20system%20integrates%20rainfall%20forecasts%20from%20an%20AI-based%20forecasting%20model%20tailored%20to%20Gorakhpur.%20These%20rainfall%20forecasts%20are%20then%20used%20to%20forecast%20the%20waterlogging%20locations%20in%20the%20city.%20Forecasts%20are%20delivered%20at%20ward-level%20resolution%2C%20helping%20anticipate%20rainfall%20and%20flood%20zones%20up%20to%2024%20hours%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrepare%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20hinges%20on%20these%20predictions.%20Municipal%20teams%20conduct%20pre-rain%20drain%20clean-up%20operations%2C%20schedule%20pump%20maintenance%2C%20and%20pre-position%20mobile%20pumps%20and%20suction%20machines.%20A%20day%20before%20forecasted%20rainfall%2C%20officials%20receive%20detailed%20preparedness%20reports%20while%20UFMC%C2%A0%20broadcasts%20alerts%20and%20instructions%20to%20the%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPushparaj%20emphasises%20the%20difference%2C%20%E2%80%9CWith%20advanced%20notice%2C%20we%20deploy%20pumps%20and%20crews%20ahead%20of%20flooding.%20Instead%20of%20scrambling%20after%20streets%20are%20submerged%2C%20we%20are%20organising%20before%20the%20deluge%20arrives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cstrong%3EProtect%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20stage%20begins%20when%20rain%20hits.%20The%20real-time%20DSS%20tracks%20water%20levels%2C%20pump%20activity%2C%20and%20team%20movements.%20Communication%20between%20the%20control%20room%20and%20field%20teams%20flows%20continuously%20through%20walkie-talkies%20and%20WhatsApp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20Gorakhpur%E2%80%99s%2025%20pumping%20stations%2C%2021%20have%20been%20automated%20via%20SCADA%20(Supervisory%20Control%20and%20Data%20Acquisition)%20technology.%20This%20allows%20engineers%20and%20staff%20to%20operate%20pumps%20remotely%20from%20the%20control%20room%20%E2%80%94%20significantly%20reducing%20delays%20and%20improving%20drainage%20efficiency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECitizen%20grievances%20logged%20through%20the%20grievance%20portal%20feed%20directly%20into%20operational%20planning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T121340.915_11zon-1754981038.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Municipal%20teams%20conduct%20pre-rain%20drain%20clean-up%20operations%2C%20schedule%20pump%20maintenance%2C%20and%20pre-position%20mobile%20pumps%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T121340.915_11zon-1754981038.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T121340.915_11zon-1754981038-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T121340.915_11zon-1754981038-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T121340.915_11zon-1754981038-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T121340.915_11zon-1754981038-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-485285%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMunicipal%20teams%20conduct%20pre-rain%20drain%20clean-up%20operations%2C%20schedule%20pump%20maintenance%2C%20and%20pre-position%20mobile%20pumps%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheshadri%20remarks%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20the%20integration%20of%20real-time%20data%2C%20automated%20pump%20control%2C%20and%20direct%20community%20inputs%20that%20creates%20a%20responsive%20ecosystem.%20This%20coordination%20is%20exactly%20why%20we%20are%20seeing%20quicker%20action%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20reduced%20flood-related%20damage%20across%20the%20city.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Cem%3ESafayi%20%3C%2Fem%3EInspector%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CRather%20than%20chasing%20complaints%20after%20chaos%20begins%2C%20we%20now%20receive%20early%20alerts%20that%20allow%20us%20to%20act%20before%20flooding%20even%20starts.%20Based%20on%20predictions%20from%20the%20system%2C%20we%20reach%20vulnerable%20hotspots%20at%20least%20a%20day%20in%20advance%2C%20mobilising%20sanitation%20workers%20to%20clean%20drains%2C%20clear%20blockages%2C%20and%20ensure%20pumps%20are%20operational.%20If%20required%2C%20we%20also%20deploy%20mobile%20pumps%20to%20reinforce%20these%20efforts.%20This%20proactive%20coordination%20does%20not%20just%20save%20time%2C%20it%20prevents%20water%20from%20entering%20homes%20and%20ultimately%20helps%20protect%20lives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStrong%20leadership%20made%20it%20possible%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmbedding%20such%20a%20system%20requires%20committed%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMayor%20Dr.%20Manglesh%20Kumar%20Srivastava%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Urban%20Flood%20Management%20System%20gives%20us%20tools%20to%20anticipate%20floods%20and%20act%20proactively%2C%20not%20only%20protecting%20properties%20but%20restoring%20civic%20trust.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMunicipal%20Commissioner%20Gaurav%20Singh%20Sogarwal%20elaborates%2C%20%E2%80%9CRealigning%20city%20operations%2C%20deploying%20predictive%20systems%2C%20and%20involving%20citizens%20via%20our%20dedicated%20grievance%20portal%20represent%20institutional%20and%20cultural%20change.%20Throughout%20this%20journey%2C%20the%20team%20from%20Canarys%20has%20consistently%20supported%20us%20with%20hands-on%20collaboration%2C%20training%2C%20and%20real-time%20guidance.%20Their%20presence%20has%20been%20important%20in%20making%20this%20change%20both%20possible%20and%20sustainable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20partnership%20to%20full%20operation%3A%20A%20disciplined%20timeline%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20began%20in%202023%20to%202024%2C%20when%20Gorakhpur%E2%80%99s%20municipal%20leaders%20partnered%20with%20Canarys%20to%20shift%20from%20reactive%20flood%20response%20to%20proactive%20intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20in%20April%202024%2C%20the%20ideation%20phase%20was%20launched%2C%20outlining%20goals%20like%20predictive%20monitoring%2C%20process%20automation%2C%20inter-agency%20coordination%2C%20and%20citizen%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%20May%20and%20August%202024%2C%20the%20design%20and%20activation%20phase%20took%20shape.%20Canarys%20brought%20in%20expertise%20in%20hydrometeorological%20modelling%2C%20real-time%20monitoring%2C%20and%20automation.%20IoT-enabled%20sensors%2C%20cloud-based%20analytics%2C%20and%20rainfall-to-response%20simulations%20were%20implemented.%20Simultaneously%2C%20the%20UFMC%20was%20established%20to%20act%20as%20a%20real-time%20operations%20hub.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T121641.599_11zon-1754981216.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Urban%20Flood%20Management%20System%20was%20inaugurated%20recently%2C%20and%20it%20is%20yet%20to%20see%20more%20impact%20in%20the%20coming%20years%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T121641.599_11zon-1754981216.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T121641.599_11zon-1754981216-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T121641.599_11zon-1754981216-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T121641.599_11zon-1754981216-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T121641.599_11zon-1754981216-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-485292%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Urban%20Flood%20Management%20System%20was%20inaugurated%20recently%2C%20and%20it%20is%20yet%20to%20see%20more%20impact%20in%20the%20coming%20years%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20implementation%20phase%20began%20in%20September%202024%2C%20with%20sensors%20deployed%20citywide%2C%20automation%20integrated%20into%20pump%20systems%2C%20and%20real-time%20coordination%20tools%20like%20WhatsApp%20and%20walkie-talkies%20introduced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20late%202024%20into%20early%202025%2C%20the%20system%20was%20further%20optimised.%20Predictive%20models%20became%20sharper%2C%20the%20citizen%20grievance%20portal%20and%20the%20toll-free%20helpline%20numbers%20were%20rolled%20out%2C%20and%20community%20participation%20increased%20%E2%80%94%20marking%20Gorakhpur%E2%80%99s%20shift%20from%20reactive%20pumping%20to%20intelligent%20flood%20resilience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EResults%20that%20speak%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20has%20been%20visible%20both%20in%20numbers%20and%20lives%20saved%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EResponse%20times%20dropped%20from%2010-12%20hours%20to%20under%201.5-2%20hours.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPump%20downtime%20decreased%20by%20over%2060%25.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPre-monsoon%20drain%20cleaning%20covered%20over%2095%25%20of%20the%20targeted%20areas.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFlood%20forecast%20accuracy%20remained%20above%2080%25%20for%2024-hour%20predictions.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOver%20250%20citizen%20complaints%20were%20recorded%3B%20more%20than%2070%25%20resolved%20within%20hours.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOverall%20system%20efficiency%20improved%20by%2065%25%2C%20boosting%20municipal%20response%20capacity.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERatna%20Devi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%202022%2C%20whenever%20it%20rained%20heavily%2C%20our%20home%20would%20flood.%20Water%20would%20enter%20the%20kitchen%20and%20the%20living%20room.%20But%20after%20the%20system%20was%20deployed%20in%20our%20area%2C%20everything%20changed.%20We%20got%20timely%20warnings%2C%20the%20pumps%20were%20switched%20on%20even%20before%20the%20rain%20peaked%2C%20and%20even%20if%20some%20water%20did%20enter%20the%20street%2C%20it%20drained%20away%20within%20an%20hour.%20We%20finally%20felt%20like%20the%20city%20was%20prepared%20to%20combat%20prolonged%20rainfall.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20lies%20ahead%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20Mayor%20Srivastava%20envisions%20a%20more%20resilient%20Gorakhpur.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20expand%20this%20Urban%20Flood%20Management%20System%2C%20deploy%20more%20sensors%2C%20and%20strengthen%20community%20outreach.%20Our%20goal%20is%20to%20set%20a%20national%20standard%20for%20flood-ready%20cities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMunicipal%20Commissioner%20Sogarwal%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20experience%20shows%20how%20leadership%2C%20technology%2C%20and%20citizen%20engagement%20can%20surmount%20the%20toughest%20urban%20challenges.%20We%20hope%20Gorakhpur%E2%80%99s%20journey%20inspires%20others.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGorakhpur%E2%80%99s%20Urban%20Flood%20Management%20System%20stands%20as%20proof%20of%20what%E2%80%99s%20possible%20when%20smart%20technology%2C%20civic%20leadership%2C%20and%20community%20collaboration%20come%20together.%20Today%2C%20monsoon%20no%20longer%20spells%20panic%20%E2%80%94%20but%20preparedness.%20And%20this%20is%20just%20the%20beginning%3B%20the%20true%20impact%20will%20unfold%20in%20the%20years%20to%20come%20as%20the%20project%20continues%20to%20expand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERatna%E2%80%AFDevi%E2%80%99s%20words%20now%20carry%20hope%20instead%20of%20fear.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20no%20longer%20feel%20scared%20when%20the%20rains%20come.%20Our%20city%20is%20awake%2C%20listening%2C%20and%20ready%20to%20protect%20us.%20This%20is%20the%20future%20we%20always%20hoped%20for.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20pictures%20courtesy%20Canarys%20Automations%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1756204200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T115631.482_11zon-1754980008.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D485239%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Once%20plagued%20by%20severe%20monsoon%20flooding%2C%20Gorakhpur%20has%20transformed%20its%20disaster%20response.%20With%20support%20from%20the%20Gorakhpur%20Municipal%20Corporation%20and%20tech%20solutions%20by%20Canarys%2C%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20flood%20warning%20system%20now%20helps%20residents%20act%20within%20two%20hours%20%E2%80%94%20instead%20of%2